      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis power-law model and turbulence closure must be justified against literature and sensitivity-tested for the VAD flow regime.",
      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model selected without sensitivity study on exponent values; turbulence model selection not justified for rotating machinery regime. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
