      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must be characterised with probability distributions and propagated through Monte Carlo UQ at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on only three of nine input parameters; remaining parameters treated as deterministic without justification. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
